 ? A pet is not unique , but mearly another form of an ability that many other classes get. Same with our damage shields. Ours are stronger , but not unique.<br><br>I believe the magician is a fairly ballenced class. We come with a built in tank , good nuking ability , good roleplaying oppertunities , and a fair bit of useful &quot;other&quot; spells (inviso , waterbreathing , levi , etc.) , but I want to see something unique.<br><br> Help me out , what is unique about a magician ? What can we offer that no one else can ? I am not whining about my magician ; I will not stop playing a magician and start up a ranger. I don't want a &quot;superman&quot; spell , just something unique.<br><br>Fadacles I , lvl 20 human magician<br>&quot;What , do I have a 'kick me' sign on my back or something ?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> ahrum</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br> <font color=#000033>(4/10/00 8:11:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylummagician.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> magicain</span><hr size=1> we are the only truly self-sufficiant class in the game. we can summon food and water(i know druids can too) we can summon weapons and ammo. we dont need components for spells like levitate. waterstone is invaluable to me.(saved my butt plenty). at 39 we can deal out over 600dd and thats not counting the pet.i think were pretty unique and share the best class with necros only <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ujolcen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jolcen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t d00d!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/13/02 2:43:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylummagician.showAddRep