 options when it comes to pets of any class. Sure towards the very end necros get a monk and rogue type pet but mages can summon 4 kinds of pets from the very beginning. Your pets deal out extreme damage. I was in a group with a 51 mage killing hgs for fun and profit and as a 45 druid I couldnt steal agro from the pet no matter how hard I nuked! It was insane watching the elemental outdamaging me nearly every time. Sure you have a hard time towards the end game of joining pickup groups and a limited role at raids but every class has a limited raid role really. Warriors &quot;just&quot; stand there and keep agro clerics &quot;just&quot; heal rezz and buff hp, shaman usually &quot;just&quot; slow, enchanters &quot;just&quot; clarity and cc, wizards &quot;just&quot; nuke lol I could go on but this post is long enough as it is. Instead of worrying about how &quot;limited&quot; and &quot;non unique&quot; just have fun knowing that you have a challenging yet fun class to play and dont worry about other classes unless you happen to be grouped with them.<br><br>Traab &quot;Love Machine&quot; Fellhammer<br>Human Mob Compactor of the 31st Cycle<br>And Almost Too Sexy To Live!<br><br>&quot;Man my posts just keep popping up everywhere!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylummagician.showPrevMessage?topicID=20.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylummagician.showNextMessage?topicID=20.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylummagician.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=12><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/bluesparty/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylummagician.emailToFriend?topicID=20.topic><img s